---
import SectionWrapper from '../SectionWrapper.astro';
import Button from '../Button.astro';
---
<div class="fear-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
<SectionWrapper bg="base" id="ai-analysis" class="fear-section">
  <!-- Headline block -->
  <p class="section-label">// AI FEAR ANALYSIS // RUNNING DIAGNOSTIC</p>
  <h2 class="fear-headline">
    <span>&gt; What&rsquo;s keeping you from using AI.</span>
    <span>&gt; And what the data actually says.</span>
  </h2>

  <!-- Fear vs Fact table -->
  <div class="table-card" role="table" aria-label="Fear versus fact comparison">
    <!-- Column headers -->
    <div class="table-header" role="row">
      <span class="col-header" role="columnheader">[FEAR]</span>
      <span class="col-header" role="columnheader">[FACT]</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Row 1 -->
    <div class="table-row" role="row">
      <div class="cell cell-fear" role="cell">
        <span class="mobile-label">[FEAR]</span>
        &ldquo;I&rsquo;ll pick the wrong tool and waste money.&rdquo;
      </div>
      <div class="cell cell-fact" role="cell">
        <span class="mobile-label">[FACT]</span>
        47% of owners struggle to choose the right AI. That&rsquo;s a diagnosis problem. Our job is to solve it.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Row 2 -->
    <div class="table-row" role="row">
      <div class="cell cell-fear" role="cell">
        <span class="mobile-label">[FEAR]</span>
        &ldquo;AI doesn&rsquo;t apply to my type of business.&rdquo;
      </div>
      <div class="cell cell-fact" role="cell">
        <span class="mobile-label">[FACT]</span>
        82% of micro-business owners say this, then adopt AI within 6 months. The framing was wrong, not the fit.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Row 3 -->
    <div class="table-row" role="row">
      <div class="cell cell-fear" role="cell">
        <span class="mobile-label">[FEAR]</span>
        &ldquo;It will replace my team.&rdquo;
      </div>
      <div class="cell cell-fact" role="cell">
        <span class="mobile-label">[FACT]</span>
        64% of owners don&rsquo;t believe AI will replace jobs in their industry. Most use it for tasks, not people.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Row 4 -->
    <div class="table-row" role="row">
      <div class="cell cell-fear" role="cell">
        <span class="mobile-label">[FEAR]</span>
        &ldquo;It won&rsquo;t sound like me.&rdquo;
      </div>
      <div class="cell cell-fact" role="cell">
        <span class="mobile-label">[FACT]</span>
        Off-the-shelf AI won&rsquo;t. We train it on your data, your voice, your FAQs. Then it does.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Row 5 -->
    <div class="table-row" role="row">
      <div class="cell cell-fear" role="cell">
        <span class="mobile-label">[FEAR]</span>
        &ldquo;I don&rsquo;t have time to figure this out.&rdquo;
      </div>
      <div class="cell cell-fact" role="cell">
        <span class="mobile-label">[FACT]</span>
        Small businesses using AI save 5.6 hrs/week per person. You recoup setup time in week one.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Status line -->
  <p class="status-line">
    STATUS: <span class="status-ok">[OK]</span> FEARS ARE DATA PROBLEMS. NOT BLOCKERS
  </p>

  <!-- AI adoption stats -->
  <div class="stats-section">
    <p class="stats-label">// AI ADOPTION // THE NUMBERS</p>

    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat-block">
        <span class="stat-number">98%</span>
        <span class="stat-desc">of small businesses plan to use AI tools this year</span>
        <span class="stat-source">Goldman Sachs 10,000 Small Businesses 2025</span>
      </div>

      <div class="stat-block">
        <span class="stat-number">5.6 hrs</span>
        <span class="stat-desc">saved per employee per week with targeted AI automation</span>
        <span class="stat-source">QuickBooks SMB AI Survey 2025</span>
      </div>

      <div class="stat-block">
        <span class="stat-number">47%</span>
        <span class="stat-desc">of owners say choosing the right AI tool is the hardest part</span>
        <span class="stat-source">ICIC AI in Business 2025</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="stats-footnote">
      // Goldman Sachs 10,000 Small Businesses 2025 &middot; ICIC AI in Business 2025<br />
      // QuickBooks 2025 SMB AI Survey &middot; 2026 Small Business AI Outlook Report
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="fear-cta">
    <Button variant="primary" href="#diagnostic">WE HANDLE THE AI. YOU RUN THE BUSINESS. &gt;</Button>
  </div>
</SectionWrapper>

<style>
  /* Amber divider rule at top */
  .fear-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.15);
  }

  /* Section label - monospace comment format */
  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  /* Headline - > prefixed, pixel font */
  .fear-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-pixel);
    font-size: var(--step-3);
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .fear-headline span {
    display: block;
  }

  .fear-headline span:first-child {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .fear-headline span:last-child {
    color: var(--text-accent-muted);
  }

  /* ── Table card ── */
  .table-card {
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-8);
    background: oklch(0.16 0.025 85);
    border: 1px solid oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.4);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Column headers */
  .table-header {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    border-bottom: 1px solid oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.25);
    padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-6);
  }

  .col-header {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .col-header:last-child {
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
  }

  /* Table rows */
  .table-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    border-bottom: 1px solid oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.1);
    transition: background 100ms var(--ease-ui);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }

  .table-row:hover {
    background: oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.06);
  }

  .table-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  /* Cells */
  .cell {
    padding: var(--space-5) var(--space-6);
  }

  .cell-fear {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    border-right: 1px solid oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.25);
  }

  .cell-fact {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: oklch(0.82 0.04 85);
  }

  /* Mobile labels - hidden on desktop */
  .mobile-label {
    display: none;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  /* ── Status line ── */
  .status-line {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--1);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .status-ok {
    color: var(--success);
  }

  /* ── Stats section ── */
  .stats-section {
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-12);
  }

  .stats-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .stat-block {
    background: oklch(0.16 0.025 85);
    border: 1px solid oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-family: var(--font-pixel);
    font-size: var(--step-3);
    color: var(--primary);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .stat-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: oklch(0.88 0.06 62);
  }

  .stat-source {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .stats-footnote {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
  }

  /* ── CTA ── */
  .fear-cta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  /* ── Responsive: tablet ── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .fear-headline {
      font-size: var(--step-2);
    }

    /* Stack table rows vertically */
    .table-header {
      display: none;
    }

    .table-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cell-fear {
      border-right: none;
      border-bottom: none;
      background: oklch(0.18 0.05 85);
      padding-bottom: var(--space-3);
    }

    .cell-fact {
      padding-top: var(--space-3);
    }

    .mobile-label {
      display: block;
    }

    /* Stats grid stacks on tablet */
    .stats-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-4);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .fear-headline {
      font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 1.1rem + 0.75vw, 1.5rem);
    }

    .cell-fear {
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .cell-fact {
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .stat-number {
      font-size: var(--step-2);
    }
  }
</style>
